query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS assessmentResponses (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  assessmentId INT NOT NULL,
  questionId INT NOT NULL,
  answerValue INT NOT NULL,
  answerLabel VARCHAR(100),
  answeredBy INT NOT NULL,
  answeredAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX assessment_responses_assessment_idx (assessmentId),
  INDEX assessment_responses_question_idx (questionId),
  UNIQUE KEY assessment_responses_unique (assessmentId, questionId),
  FOREIGN KEY (assessmentId) REFERENCES capabilityAssessments(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  FOREIGN KEY (questionId) REFERENCES assessmentQuestions(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  FOREIGN KEY (answeredBy) REFERENCES users(id)
)
